On 30 Jun 2020 (as of midnight 1 Jul 2020):
- 3 new cases of confirmed infections (all locally acquired cases in Beijing municipality), 2 new cases of suspected infection (both imported cases in Shanghai), and no deaths.
- A total of 1918 imported cases have been reported.
- 83 534 confirmed cases and 4634 deaths; 78 479 recovered and discharged from hospital; 762 744 close contacts with infected patients, and 6479 are under medical observation.
- 3 new asymptomatic cases (all imported cases); 1 locally acquired asymptomatic cases confirmed as symptomatic; 100 asymptomatic cases under medical observation (including 63 imported cases).
- 1205 cases in Hong Kong [an increase of 2 cases since 29 Jun 2020], 46 in Macau [same as 29 Jun 2020].

